{"title":"HipoacusiaAUGE iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología/HipoacusiaAUGE iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Hipoacusia Bilateral AUGE\\N— 65 años y más","guid":"CKpdWys6YcVCVbPCjNWiOg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición y\\NEpidemiología","guid":"2kAd72mqxxYtNHDs9fOlbA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"PRESBIACUSIA = hipoacusia neurosensorial bilateral simétrica por envejecimiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Causa MÁS FRECUENTE de sordera en persona mayor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Epidemiología Chile\\N(ENS 2009-2010)","guid":"yNjL4rUpN6fjD3x1oavsWA","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Autopercepción hipoacusia en >65a → 52%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"Prevalencia mundial: ~40% en >65a (↑ con edad)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"Impacto clínico\\N(GIGANTE\\NGERIÁTRICO)","guid":"6xlj1-8zoGEEem1y2-BGng","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Depresión y aislamiento social","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Deterioro cognitivo\\N→ DEMENCIA","guid":"MXMn8u4Wc9QefWxAd-uZPA","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Factor modificable → 9% riesgo demencia atribuible (Lancet Commission 2020)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"ACHIEVE Trial 2025: rehabilitación auditiva ↓ declive cognitivo 62% en alto riesgo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"7","text":"Deterioro calidad de vida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"7","text":"↑ riesgo caídas y accidentes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"7","text":"Compromiso de la autonomía","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Cambios degenerativos del oído interno (cóclea, nervio auditivo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"Mecanismos\\Nhipoacusia-cognición","guid":"koRTIiUy2aR8v5cObRUDzA","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"Hipótesis carga cognitiva → esfuerzo auditivo agota reservas cognitivas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"Hipótesis causa común → neurodegeneración paralela","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"Hipótesis cascada → privación sensorial → atrofia cortex auditivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"17","text":"Hipótesis sobrediagnóstico → confusión con deterioro cognitivo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"15","text":"Cambios\\Nhistopatológicos","guid":"x9e-JNW27EsmVvrr-4PPEA","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"↓ células ciliadas cocleares externas (frecuencias agudas primero)","guid":"Zh9zAxFPuRT-9o26Cvtapg","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"Atrofia estría vascular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"↓ neuronas espirales del ganglio","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Tipos de\\Nhipoacusia","guid":"arwlAlw_UyWY0RVxr5FlGg","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"Conductiva → oído externo/medio (reversible frecuente)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"NEUROSENSORIAL → oído interno/nervio auditivo (más común en presbiacusia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"Mixta → ambas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"26","text":"Clasificación OMS por\\NPromedio Tonal Puro (PTP)","guid":"6JTDWNwavhJRiRBVrIS8uA","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Normal → ≤25 dB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"Leve → 26-40 dB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"MODERADA → 41-60 dB (UMBRAL GARANTÍA GES)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"Severa → 61-80 dB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"31","text":"Profunda → >80 dB","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"0","text":"Prevención\\NPrimaria","guid":"pDMhXmKKeBwBrk-eVSJ3fA","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"CONTROL ruido → protección auditiva en ambientes ruidosos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"CONTROL factores de\\Nriesgo cardiovascular","guid":"kZQqg1n6WIkGlR1zFpiCAA","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"DM → control glicémico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"Dislipidemia → tratamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"39","text":"Tabaquismo → suspensión","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"37","text":"Fármacos OTOTÓXICOS\\N(evaluar riesgo/beneficio)","guid":"D1b8R0AcCR4t6-nmQlDFjg","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Aminoglucósidos → especialmente con ERC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"Diuréticos de asa → furosemida altas dosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"Salicilatos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"43","text":"AINEs → uso crónico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"43","text":"Platinos (quimioterapia)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"37","text":"Manejo patología ótica → tratar otitis, derivar crónicas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"0","text":"Tamizaje y\\NSospecha\\NDiagnóstica","guid":"V-XNFa_Rb8_IH60EraHx-Q","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"EMPAM (Examen Medicina\\NPreventiva Adulto Mayor)","guid":"_e1vBe9Qm9xIL5iBw5Y_oQ","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"Pregunta anual: ¿Tiene usted alguna dificultad para escuchar?","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"Sensibilidad autorreporte → 71-93% para hipoacusia moderada (≥40 dB)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"50","text":"Anamnesis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Evolución temporal (insidiosa en presbiacusia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"Tinnitus asociado → frecuente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"Vértigo → descartar patología laberíntica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"54","text":"Impacto funcional: conversaciones grupales, TV a alto volumen","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"50","text":"Examen físico\\NOBLIGATORIO","guid":"wnJfKk8nmbXopWOSSy2sDg","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"OTOSCOPÍA → primer paso siempre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"Tapón de cerumen → hasta 30% de AM con hipoacusia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"Causa reversible MÁS FRECUENTE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Extracción = intervención costo-efectiva en geriatría","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"59","text":"Patología oído medio → OMA, OMS, OMCS","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"50","text":"Cuestionario HHIE-S (Hearing\\NHandicap Inventory Elderly-Screening)","guid":"e5mQRIauzDXDsCbIj3JXcA","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"10 ítems (social y emocional)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"Puntaje ≥10 → repercusión social significativa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"Indicación relativa audífono si PTP 35-40 dB","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"0","text":"Confirmación\\NDiagnóstica","guid":"PydsYF3sI-GSD8DCKpbrtQ","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"AUDIOMETRÍA TONAL\\N(gold standard)","guid":"MoYk9Wlyl5cCgqik0o2LhA","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"Cámara silente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"PTP = promedio umbrales en 500, 1000, 2000 y 4000 Hz","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"Curva descendente → pérdida preferente frecuencias agudas (típica presbiacusia)","guid":"gT1fpm8dSAvOo7xFaeCL1w","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"69","text":"Exámenes\\Ncomplementarios","guid":"TcoPEdO-7RDsRgefb8pc4A","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"LOGOAUDIOMETRÍA","guid":"qiLpvoMyuF-QwhZZiS-Lcw","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Evalúa discriminación de la palabra (no solo umbral)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"Oír sin entender → procesamiento central alterado → impacto en rehabilitación","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"74","text":"IMPEDANCIOMETRÍA → función oído medio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"Timpanograma + reflejo estapedial","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"69","text":"Quién lo realiza","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Otorrinolaringólogo (especialista confirmador)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"Tecnólogo Médico / Fonoaudiólogo (audiometría)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento —\\NIndicación de\\NAudífono\\N(Garantía GES)","guid":"vN9qrevySiGDBVgrf7ETag","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"INDICACIÓN\\NABSOLUTA","guid":"_cCJPsKtzuukVcfx4H4RIw","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"PTP ≥40 dB en MEJOR OÍDO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"→ Audífono uniaural (GES)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"83","text":"INDICACIÓN RELATIVA\\N(zona gris)","guid":"x7IdIM9RMKv8xVkL7yx9Fg","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"PTP 35-40 dB en mejor oído","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"+ HHIE-S ≥10 (repercusión social)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"87","text":"→ Audífono si ambos criterios presentes","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"83","text":"Características\\Ndel audífono","guid":"Rz63rubLXB2XvSogha9Nsg","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Digital con múltiples micrófonos → mayor satisfacción","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"Canal abierto → indicado en curvas descendentes","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"83","text":"Segundo audífono","guid":"","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"Contralateral → tras 1 año de buena adherencia con el primero","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"83","text":"Evaluación geriátrica\\Npara indicación","guid":"8isguitbSANVO4eW2z0cSA","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Motivación del paciente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"Destreza manual → manejo dispositivo y pilas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"Estado cognitivo → comprensión y uso","guid":"N9PU8XmYMPOizvDwKx0WFQ","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"96","text":"Red de apoyo → cuidador que apoye adherencia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"83","text":"Implante\\Ncoclear","guid":"VGFrTxm18jrLqheEarJk8w","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"Hipoacusia severa-profunda bilateral refractaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"Edad NO contraindica per se","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"Neuroplasticidad ↓ con edad → mejores resultados si CI precoz","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y\\NRehabilitación","guid":"ejJP5uZdxjWfnSd60dx5ww","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"Adaptación del\\Naudífono","guid":"-hfucTp2Dj3Rv8UpfcLq4g","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"Educación manejo dispositivo y pilas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"106","text":"Confort físico y auditivo → sin dolor, sin acoples","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"105","text":"Rehabilitación auditiva\\N(enfoque integral)","guid":"SQasHLJL0uQqcFR7oySI3Q","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"MANEJO DE EXPECTATIVAS → audífono no restaura audición normal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"ACE (Educación\\NComunicativa Activa)","guid":"mIhWETJbND7paRcmTXjTYQ","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"Estrategias situaciones difíciles (grupos, ruido)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"111","text":"Lectura labial complementaria","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"109","text":"Participación familiar → cuidadores → ↑ resultados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"109","text":"Rehabilitación GRUPAL → reduce estigma, comparte experiencias","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"105","text":"Adherencia —\\NPROBLEMA MAYOR","guid":"uVKXshnUTF2FRaI11XT1pw","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"Uso correcto ~40-50% en Chile (estudios nacionales)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"116","text":"Causas frecuentes\\Nde abandono","guid":"3hAr6lMcSqLmQoU9jLhfDw","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"Manejo difícil → destreza manual disminuida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"Intolerancia al ruido ambiental amplificado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"118","text":"Estigma social","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"118","text":"Deterioro cognitivo → olvida usarlo","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"123","parent":"105","text":"Controles","guid":"","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"Fonoaudiólogo/Tecnólogo Médico → anual","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":"Otorrinolaringólogo + audiometría → cada 5 años","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"fYoD1j1VP12xfc1cIjqgbg","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"Hipoacusia = factor riesgo MODIFICABLE para demencia → ACHIEVE 2025: ↓62% declive cognitivo en alto riesgo con HA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"Tapón de cerumen → primer diagnóstico a descartar SIEMPRE antes de derivar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"126","text":"OIGO PERO NO ENTIENDO → logoaudiometría alterada → compromiso procesamiento central → HA con menor beneficio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"126","text":"Indicación audífono requiere VGI → evaluar cognición, destreza, motivación y red de apoyo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"126","text":"Adherencia ~40-50% → seguimiento activo es TAN importante como la indicación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"126","text":"Fármacos ototóxicos en AM hospitalizado → aminoglucósidos + furosemida altas dosis con ERC = vigilar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"126","text":"Hipoacusia + deterioro cognitivo en demencia → HA ↓ síntomas depresivos (b=-0.74, IC95% -1.48 a -0.01)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"126","text":"Diagnóstico diferencial con hipoacusia conductiva → otoscopía SIEMPRE en la consulta","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"0","text":"VER\\NTAMBIÉN","guid":"YkxS8vVaW36a9iCSyC0SBw","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"→ Deterioro Cognitivo Leve (Geriatría-Cognitivo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"→ Delirium UCI (Geriatría-UCI)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"→ Deprescripción AM (Farmacología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"135","text":"→ Síndrome de Menière (ORL)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"135","text":"→ Valoración Geriátrica Integral (Geriatría)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"1. MINSAL. Guía Clínica AUGE: Hipoacusia bilateral en personas de 65 años y más que requieren uso de Audífono. Santiago: MINSAL; 2013.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"2. Uchida Y, et al. Age-related hearing loss and cognitive decline. Auris Nasus Larynx. 2019;46(1):1-9. doi:10.1016/j.anl.2018.08.010","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"141","text":"3. Pike JR, et al. Cognitive benefits of hearing intervention vary by risk of cognitive decline: ACHIEVE trial. Alzheimers Dement. 2025;21(5):e70156. doi:10.1002/alz.70156","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"141","text":"4. Atef RZ, et al. Impact of Hearing Aids on Progression of Cognitive Decline, Depression, and QoL. J Alzheimers Dis. 2023;92(2):629-638. doi:10.3233/JAD-220938","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"141","text":"5. Lazard DS, et al. Plasticity after hearing rehabilitation in the aging brain. Trends Hear. 2023;27:23312165231156412. doi:10.1177/23312165231156412","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"141","text":"6. Spanke AM. Age-related hearing loss: Causes, treatment, and care. Nursing. 2025;55(12):26-34. doi:10.1097/NSG.0000000000000291","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"141","text":"7. Livingston G, et al. Dementia prevention, intervention, and care. Lancet. 2020;396(10248):413-446.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":148,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"ORL","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología","filename":"HipoacusiaAUGE iPad","id":"map_1564","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"HipoacusiaAUGE iPad"}